{"tid":170272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可以逃得去邊","createTime":"2017-03-24T15:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T15:37:39.000Z","uid":90290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18ff8f3d5c86607d9abb579efa2ff0312d71671c","tid":170272,"uid":90290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"個個都話移民，查實移左又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 世上冇烏托邦，移民去邊你都會不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好鐘意睇個D平衡時空回到過去既電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大多數都係表達就算你有不滿，後悔，你可以有take two，跟住都係會有新既不滿同後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以話我港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我已經接受左現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算個個都買得起樓，就算條街冇曬新移民自由行，到時都繼續有新既社會問題，你都會有下一個欲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日話移民既人只係係到比較其他國家有同自己國家冇既野，咁樣比較你永遠都唔會幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算你移左民，你都可能習慣唔到文化，可能都係買唔到樓，可能治安麻麻每日都擔驚受怕，其實你走唔走，不滿都係會佔你人生既一半，你離開到香港，唔代表離開到不安同恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隨遇而安啦。<br />\n<br />\n第一次出post sorry for1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}